{
  "stem": "21812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we heard it on the-- maybe on the radio, on the-- communications were not the way they are today.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we heard it on the radio, maybe in the newspaper, or maybe just by word of mouth what was going on, that vom Rath had killed the German attache, I think, in Paris.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what's precipitated it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- I mean, the-- the Jewish man had killed vom Rath in Paris.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we knew that had happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We knew that had happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they were beginning, I think, even immediately-- I don't know what the time frame was between the killing and Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know how many-- whether one or two days passed or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that there was already talk and, you know, with the grape vine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it happened very quickly, because the town is not that large, and-- and rumors spread very quickly, that they were rounding up men for a first-- that was the first time-- Jewish men and putting them into concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so the-- the morning, and then maybe they burned-- and I don't remember whether they burned the synagogues at night or whether they did it on-- I think they burned them the day before, or the night before.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And evidently, my father must have been instrumental, and I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But as I said before, the-- the janitor in our building, in my grandmother's building, was a Social Democrat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] my father must have, I would assume, gone to her and said, we have to hide.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so then she suggested that he-- he and I should go into the coal cellar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- excuse me-- and if we-- if she had been a Nazi, she would have said no.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
